==Chinese==
===[[Mandarin]]===
[[Pinyin]]: jī tóng yā jiǎng

===Etymology===
Literally: a chicken talking to a duck

===Idiom===
'''[[雞]][[同]][[鴨]][[講]]'''

# mutually unintelligable; unable to understand one another
# [we/they] [are/were] talking about two different things; [we/they] [are/were] getting [our/their] wires crossed
# to talk past each other

===Alternate forms===
[[鸡同鸭讲]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

